com.github.dkharrat.nexusdata.metamodel

Class ObjectModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.dkharrat.nexusdata.metamodel.ObjectModel

  • public class ObjectModel
extends Object
    An ObjectModel represents the collection of Entitys that defines the types of objects that exist in a persistence store.

      • getVersion

        public int getVersion()
        Returns the model version. Model versions are used to identify different versions of the same semantic model. When making changes to a model that has already been published and is in use, make sure to increment the version number to have persistence stores using older versions of the model to upgrade.
        Returns:
        an integer representing the model's version
